widgets_values:
Good controlnet values for InstantX merged ControlNet is around
Strength 0.7
end_percent 0.2

XLABS
Strength 0.5
end_percent 0.5

Flux ControlNets are not working as intended currently, as high values break the images. 
We are not using xlabs and instantx nodes for ease of use.

Download ControlNet Union Pro model from model manager or https://huggingface.co/Shakker-Labs/FLUX.1-dev-ControlNet-Union-Pro/resolve/main/diffusion_pytorch_model.safetensors?download=true

Currently all ControlNets use the same merged model. When newer/better individual models are released, you can replace the ControlNet models in the workflow.
Enable or disable ControlNets here if the individual fast bypasser is not functional.
Enable and disable ControlNets at the fast bypasser switch.
